Contact
public class ContactImpl
extends java.lang.Object
implements Contact

ContactImpl - Implements Contact interface A contact is a person we are making business with or may do in the future. Contacts have an ID (unique), a name (probably unique, but maybe not), and notes that the user may want to save about them.
